<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>L.I.F.E.</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all' %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application' %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Ruda:400,900,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
</head>

<body class="welcome_home">
<div class="welcome_page">

    <div class="home_logo">
      <h1>L.I.F.E.</h1>
      <small>Lessons In the Form of Experiences</small>
    </div>

    <div class="nav_bar">
        <ul class="menu">
          <li><%= link_to "Stories", stories_path, :class => "list" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "Profiles", profiles_path, :class => "list" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "Add A Story", new_story_path, :class => "list" %></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="explanation">
      <p>For many successful people, their greatest lessons were learned outside the traditional classroom setting.  With the job market becoming increasingly competitive, it is more important than ever to distinguish yourself through experiences that show your passion and individuality.  Here, we explore different paths your friends, colleagues, neighbors, and even strangers have taken to developing a more diverse set of skills and talents.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>

</html>
